<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="throw-v">throw <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /θrəʊ/    美 /θroʊ/  </p>
<p>(threw, thrown)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>抛；扔：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Throw me the ball. / Throw the ball to me.<strong>Throw_2</strong<strong> to</strong>
把球抛给我。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was thrown by a horse. 
我被马甩了下来。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>猛推；使劲撞：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She drew the curtains and <strong>threw open</strong> the windows.
她拉开窗帘，一把推开窗户。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="throw-away">throw away</h3>
<p>1.<strong>扔掉(throw out)；浪费 (金钱等)；放过 (机会等)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People are recycling many things which they would have thrown away in the past.
人们在回收利用很多他们在过去会扔掉的东西。</p><footer>2014 安徽</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>throw away the best time of one’s life 
浪费人生中的金色年华</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is the best chance you can have. Take it. Don’t throw it away. 
这是你最好的机会，把握住，别放过。</p></div>

<h3 id="throw-off">throw off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>扔掉；摆脱；匆匆脱掉 (衣服)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Throw off all your unpleasant memories. 
忘掉你所有不愉快的记忆。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He threw off his coat and started work. 
他匆忙脱下外衣，开始工作。</p></div>

<h3 id="throw-oneself-into">throw oneself into</h3>
<p>1.<strong>投身于；积极从事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As the vegetables started coming in, Dad threw himself into cooking.  
当蔬菜被送来的时候，父亲全身心地投入到烹饪当中。</p><footer>2015 四川</footer></div>

<h3 id="throw-oneself-on">throw oneself on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>扑倒在…上；完全依赖：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I threw myself on the bed in my clothes, trying to find a few moments of sleep.  
我和衣倒在床上，试图睡上一会儿。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I throw myself on your support to help me with this competition. 
我就靠你来帮我赢得这场比赛了。</p></div>

<h3 id="throw-out">throw out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>抛出；扔掉(throw away)；撵走；开除：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Protect the water environment consciously; don’t throw out peels, paper scraps, etc. 
自觉保护水环境，不要乱扔果皮、纸屑等。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ll be thrown out if you don’t pay the rent. 
如果不付房租，你就会被赶出去。</p></div>

<h3 id="throw-up">throw up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>抛起；举起：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>throw up one’s hands in fear 
恐惧地举起双手</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>thrower /'θrəʊə(r)/ n [C]   </p></div>